!.env.example
*.pem
*.key
*.p12
*.pfx
**/secrets.yaml
**/secrets.yml
**/auth

# AI agent harness state — private working memory / machine / session.
# Shared agent config IS committed: .agents/, root AGENTS.md, CLAUDE.md,
# .claude/settings.json, .claude/skills. See .agents/skills/all-aboard.
# (.codex/ is git-ignored below.)
.claude/settings.local.json
.claude/.credentials.json
.claude/history.jsonl
.claude/projects/
.claude/sessions/
.claude/shell-snapshots/
.claude/todos/
.claude/statsig/

